{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji29.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给黄炎培的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给黄炎培的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年9月1日）任之先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大示敬悉，承赠大作《红桑集》，极为感谢。南方各省有丰收之望，北方亦有此种情形，检陈华北局报告一份，可以一阅，阅后请予掷还为荷。顺致敬意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月一日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]黄炎培，字任之，中国民主建国会主要负责人。当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]指中共中央华北局1950年8月29日关于秋收、秋耕、秋种工作的指示。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":9,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":127,"page_end":127},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}